ful."}},"10":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.18","c":"وَقَالُوٓاْ","d":"waqālū","e":"And they say","i":"وَقَالُوۡٓا"},{"b":"1.7","h":"3.34","c":"أَءِذَا","d":"a-idhā","e":"Is (it) when","i":"ءَاِذَا"},{"b":"2.3","h":"4.79","c":"ضَلَلۡنَا","d":"ḍalalnā","e":"we are lost","i":"ضَلَلۡنَا"},{"b":"3.3","h":"6.63","c":"فِي","d":"fī","e":"in","i":"فِى"},{"b":"3.5","h":"7.07","c":"ٱلۡأَرۡضِ","d":"l-arḍi","e":"the earth","i":"الۡاَرۡضِ"},{"b":"4.3","h":"8.54","c":"أَءِنَّا","d":"a-innā","e":"will we","i":"ءَاِنَّا"},{"b":"5.9","h":"10.84","c":"لَفِي","d":"lafī","e":"certainly be in","i":"لَفِىۡ"},{"b":"6.4","h":"11.92","c":"خَلۡقٖ","d":"khalqin","e":"a creation","i":"خَلۡقٍ"},{"b":"7.9","h":"13.99","c":"جَدِيدِۭۚ","d":"jadīdin","e":"new","i":"جَدِيۡدٍؕ ​"},{"b":"10.5","h":"18.4","c":"بَلۡ","d":"bal","e":"Nay","i":"بَلۡ"},{"b":"10.","h":"19.09","c":"هُم","d":"hum","e":"they","i":"هُمۡ"},{"b":"12.1","h":"20.31","c":"بِلِقَآءِ","d":"biliqāi","e":"in (the) meeting","i":"بِلِقَآءِ"},{"b":"14.5","h":"23.35","c":"رَبِّهِمۡ","d":"rabbihim","e":"(of) their Lord","i":"رَبِّهِمۡ"},{"b":"15.4","h":"25.48","c":"كَٰفِرُونَ","d":"kāfirūna","e":"(are) disbelievers","i":"كٰفِرُوۡنَ"}],"a":{"g":"And they say, \"When we are lost within the earth, will we indeed be [recreated] in a new creation?\" Rather, they are, in [the matter of] the meeting with their Lord, disbelievers."}},"11":{"w":[{"b":"0.04","h":"0.45","c":"قُلۡ","d":"qul","e":"Say","i":"۞ قُلۡ"},{"b":"0.3","h":"0.89","c":"يَتَوَفَّىٰكُم","d":"yatawaffākum","e":"Will take your soul","i":"يَتَوَفّٰٮكُمۡ"},{"b":"2.7","h":"4.64","c":"مَّلَكُ","d":"malaku","e":"(the) Angel","i":"مَّلَكُ"},{"b":"3.2","h":"5.65","c":"ٱلۡمَوۡتِ","d":"l-mawti","e":"(of) the death","i":"الۡمَوۡتِ"},{"b":"4.0","h":"7.19","c":"ٱلَّذِي","d":"alladhī","e":"the one who","i":"الَّذِىۡ"},{"b":"4.7","h":"8.71","c":"وُكِّلَ","d":"wukkila","e":"has been put in charge","i":"وُكِّلَ"},{"b":"5.4","h":"10.12","c":"بِكُمۡ","d":"bikum","e":"of you","i":"بِكُمۡ"},{"b":"6.0","h":"1