ard, so return us [to the world]; we will work righteousness. Indeed, we are [now] certain.\""}},"13":{"w":[{"b":"0.06","h":"0.49","c":"وَلَوۡ","d":"walaw","e":"And if","i":"وَ لَوۡ"},{"b":"0.54","h":"1.3","c":"شِئۡنَا","d":"shi'nā","e":"We (had) willed","i":"شِئۡنَا"},{"b":"1.3","h":"2.8","c":"لَأٓتَيۡنَا","d":"laātaynā","e":"surely We (would) have given","i":"لَاٰتَيۡنَا"},{"b":"2.5","h":"5.48","c":"كُلَّ","d":"kulla","e":"every","i":"كُلَّ"},{"b":"3.2","h":"6.62","c":"نَفۡسٍ","d":"nafsin","e":"soul","i":"نَفۡسٍ"},{"b":"3.9","h":"8.07","c":"هُدَىٰهَا","d":"hudāhā","e":"its guidance","i":"هُدٰٮهَا"},{"b":"4.7","h":"10.05","c":"وَلَٰكِنۡ","d":"walākin","e":"but","i":"وَلٰـكِنۡ"},{"b":"5.7","h":"11.74","c":"حَقَّ","d":"ḥaqqa","e":"(is) true","i":"حَقَّ"},{"b":"6.3","h":"12.94","c":"ٱلۡقَوۡلُ","d":"l-qawlu","e":"the Word","i":"الۡقَوۡلُ"},{"b":"7.0","h":"14.51","c":"مِنِّي","d":"minnī","e":"from Me","i":"مِنِّىۡ"},{"b":"12.3","h":"16.27","c":"لَأَمۡلَأَنَّ","d":"la-amla-anna","e":"that I will surely fill","i":"لَاَمۡلَئَنَّ"},{"b":"14.1","h":"19.2","c":"جَهَنَّمَ","d":"jahannama","e":"Hell","i":"جَهَنَّمَ"},{"b":"15.3","h":"21.58","c":"مِنَ","d":"mina","e":"with","i":"مِنَ"},{"b":"15.9","h":"22.24","c":"ٱلۡجِنَّةِ","d":"l-jinati","e":"the jinn","i":"الۡجِنَّةِ"},{"b":"17.6","h":"24.62","c":"وَٱلنَّاسِ","d":"wal-nāsi","e":"and the men","i":"وَالنَّاسِ"},{"b":"19.3","h":"27.07","c":"أَجۡمَعِينَ","d":"ajmaʿīna","e":"together","i":"اَجۡمَعِيۡنَ"}],"a":{"g":"And if We had willed, We could have given every soul its guidance, but the word from Me will come into effect [that] \"I will surely fill Hell with jinn and people all together."}},"14":{"w":[{"b":"0.03","h":"0.55","c":"فَذُوقُواْ","d":"fadhūqū","e":"So taste","i":"فَذُوۡقُوۡا"},{"b":"0.9","h":"2.26","c":"بِمَا","d":"bimā","e":"because","i":"بِمَا"},{"b":"1.4","h":"3.36","c":"نَسِيتُمۡ","d":"nasītum","e":"you forgot","i":"نَسِيۡتُمۡ"},{"b":"2.3","h":"5.17","c":"لِقَآءَ","d":"liqāa","e":"(the) meeting","i":"لِقَآءَ"},